CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 17, 1940, pg. 20, reads: "Here they are...Lionel Hampton, the nation's No. 1 vibraharpist and Billy Rowe, as they arrived at Pittsburgh's County Airport Friday afternoon to participate in festivities incident to selecting "Miss Pittsburgh" in "Miss Bronze America" contest. - Harris Foto."
TitMainTitle: Lionel Hampton and Billy Rowe standing on steps of TWA airplane at Allegheny County Airport
